metadata.name: Twilight
metadata.description:
Twilight AKA the Lord of the Cats AKA Cat Daddy AKA Austin

A self portrait I took of myself on April 21st, 2022. This photo has achieved borderline meme status in the NFT Photography space, as it's been my profile picture all summer long. It allowed me to make connections simply because people saw this photo first before they saw the art that I make, and were interested in who I was and why I looked like a Twilight character lol
